&lt;p data-start=&quot;1824&quot; data-end=&quot;2024&quot;&gt;If you’re excited about our mission and believe you’d be a great addition to our team, submit your resume and tell us about your interests, background, and the kind of role you’re hoping to explore.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;2026&quot; data-end=&quot;2168&quot;&gt;We keep submissions on file and review them regularly as new opportunities open across the company. Thank you for your interest in Resonate.&lt;/p&gt;
