&lt;li data-start=&quot;507&quot; data-end=&quot;1398&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;859&quot; data-end=&quot;878&quot;&gt;Growth Mindset:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;You’re open to learning, feedback, and trying new things.&lt;/li&gt;
